how can i change myself i feel very down now my friends betrayed me sometimes my father's words hurt me a lot i'm years old girl without mother i was bullied by my friends long time ago mentally hurt by my father and friends my bad memories were more than good memories i i want to change myself a long time ago but i just couldn't do it when i start something i'll be distracted or lost interest very soon i feel so useless now i always ask myself what the hell am i doing all the time nothing i want to become a programmer i was learning qbasic yesterday and soon my thoughts keep myself away from what i'm doing i hope i can find some answers here to keep myself motivated and become what i want to become and forget those bad memories and my betrayed friends wow girl you have got to stop beating yourself up i know you're down and sounds like you have a reason to be down this comes from someone who understands how very disappointing parents can be sometimes it's not really about what we do but it is about what we have allowed our parents to get away with his rejection of you is causing you tremendous fear in your life you're going to have to find a way to temper that with some constructive criticism and or some unconditional acceptance from someone whom you do trust begin to surround yourself with people who do make you feel good that will cure at least the initial emotion that you re feeling then i think you need to have a serious talk with yourself if you're on the brink of understanding all this asking the questions and get your answer it is your right to put that to use take a moment really think about what you want out of life not a job not a car or even that purple sweater you saw last week what do you want do you want kids some day where do you want to live what kind of man or woman do you see for your mate what does your life look like down the road then write down what that means to you how that makes you feel when you think about it settle it in the pit of your s